name: Diamond (yellow)
description:
DIAMOND (framed purse) – ND0210yellow

The elegance this purse exudes is unbelievable! Extremely graceful, this framed clutch purse is designed to excite that stylista in you. An elegant evening bag is always in style. Its modern triangular shape effortlessly adds pizzazz to your ensemble. 

Measuring approximately: 11” frame(top), 14” base, 6” total height, this classic clutch purse will easily hold your phone, keys, lipstick and a few personal items every diva needs on a night out.

name: Toffee Tote (yellow)
description:
TOFFEE TOTE (the weekend bag) – ND0250yellow

Don’t you just love the weekend!!! Make your weekends even more lovable and colorful with our beautiful toffee weekend totes. Huge enough to carry every single thing you can imagine is needed either the beach (towels, flip flops, sun tan) or on that amazing getaway! 

Tote measures: 15” HX 4.5”base X 17”top width X 15bottom width

name: Gemstone (pink)
description:
GEMSTONE (SIGNATURE oversized) – ND0230multi

Original is the word we use to describe this elegant African print oversized pocketbook. A timeless eye candy, this purse will absolutely compliment you from head to toe with its bold feature. A blend of authentically rich ethnic colors enhanced with a single metal snap and an inside pocket, you can wear this purse to any event; just don’t forget your stilettos!

Measures: 18” x 7”
